# Design system

Spec: `apps/web/DESIGN.md`.

## Aesthetic

Government command UI — not TCG, not neon, not fantasy.

## Tokens

Use `state-*`, `faction-*`, `board-ink` from `tailwind.config.ts`. Use `lib/ui/variants.ts` for panels/buttons.

## Cards

- `components/cards/DirectiveCard.tsx` + `lib/cards/`
- Art: `public/cards/themes/*.svg` via `getCardArtSrc`

## Motion

`lib/motion/tokens.ts`, `variants.ts`, respect `MotionProvider` reduced motion.

## Scope

UI-only tasks stay in `apps/web`. Do not change engine for color tweaks.

## Forbidden

- Gacha frames, neon glows, arcade particles
- Animating card width/height on hover
- Comments explaining obvious styles
